    {
      "id": "content-004",
      "lesson_id": "intro-choice",
      "content_type": "questionnaire",
      "title": "My brief introduction",
      "content": "",
      "metadata": {
        "options": [
          "Would you like to know?",
          "Shall we move forward directly?"
        ],
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "content-005",
      "lesson_id": "intro-choice",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "I am the script created by Adi Brahma, the first Tirthankara Maharaja Shri Rishabhdev Ji.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "content-006",
      "lesson_id": "intro-choice",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "He created me while teaching his daughter Brahmi.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "content-007",
      "lesson_id": "intro-choice",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "Along with Brahmi, Maharaja Shri Rishabhdev Ji also taught 'Ank Vidya' to his other daughter Sundari.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "content-008",
      "lesson_id": "intro-choice",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "Both of them widely spread the knowledge imparted by Bhagwan Shri Rishabhdev Ji.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "content-009",
      "lesson_id": "intro-choice",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "Why was I named 'Brahmi Script'?",
      "content": "Princess Brahmi imparted the knowledge of this script to the common people, hence I was named 'Brahmi Script'.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "content-010",
      "lesson_id": "intro-choice",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "I am not a language!",
      "content": "Remember, I am not a language, but merely a writing system.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "content-011",
      "lesson_id": "intro-language-definition",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "\"The medium through which we express our feelings to one another is called 'language'.\"\nFor example – Hindi, Punjabi, Bengali, Telugu, Tamil, Gujarati, Kannada, Odia, English, etc.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "content-012",
      "lesson_id": "intro-language-definition",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "\"The medium through which any language is written is called 'script'.\"\nOr\n\"The symbols used to represent spoken sounds in written form are called a script.\"\nFor example – Hindi–Devanagari, Punjabi–Gurmukhi, Bengali–Bengali, Telugu–Telugu, Tamil–Tamil, Gujarati–Gujarati, Kannada–Kannada, Odia–Odia, English–Latin (Roman), etc.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "content-013",
      "lesson_id": "intro-specialty",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "My specialty",
      "content": "I am originally the script of the 'Prakrit language'.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "content-014",
      "lesson_id": "intro-specialty",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "However, I can be used to write any language just like Devanagari or Latin/Roman script.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "content-015",
      "lesson_id": "intro-specialty",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "And yes, let me tell you a secret.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "content-016",
      "lesson_id": "intro-specialty",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "You can make me your secret script and keep all your secrets hidden from ordinary people.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "content-017",
      "lesson_id": "intro-specialty",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "My importance",
      "content": "My vowels and consonants are similar to Devanagari (Hindi).\nI can directly connect you to Tirthankara Shri Rishabhdev Ji.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "content-018",
      "lesson_id": "intro-specialty",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "So, do not leave my side.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "content-019",
      "lesson_id": "intro-spiritual",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "I will make every effort to connect you directly with Tirthankara Rishabhdev Ji Maharaj, because now I alone remain as the true living memory of the Tirthankara.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "content-020",
      "lesson_id": "intro-spiritual",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "I know what you are thinking.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "content-021",
      "lesson_id": "intro-spiritual",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "The scriptures we have are called Jinwani, that is, the divine sound of the Jina (Tirthankara).",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "content-022",
      "lesson_id": "intro-spiritual",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "So, in a way, we all possess the direct form of the Tirthankara.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "content-023",
      "lesson_id": "intro-spiritual",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "Yes, absolutely! You are right.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "content-024",
      "lesson_id": "intro-spiritual",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "But, think once— the scriptures we have are considered and worshipped by us as Jinwani itself.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "content-025",
      "lesson_id": "intro-spiritual",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "The divine sound of the Lord was compiled by the Ganadharas, passed on to Acharyas, and through tradition only a small portion has reached us.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "content-026",
      "lesson_id": "intro-spiritual",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "But it is not the direct Jinwani; it is Jinwani in a traditional form.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "content-027",
      "lesson_id": "intro-spiritual",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "After the sacred nirvana of Bhagwan Shri Rishabhdev Ji, traversing an immeasurable span of time, I stand before you today—with memories of infinite ages, pure unbroken knowledge, and the divine heritage of Bhagwan Rishabhdev.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "content-028",
      "lesson_id": "intro-spiritual",
      "content_type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "content": "So now you understand, how I am— the living memory of the Tirthankara.",
      "metadata": {
        "buttonText": "Next"
      },
      "order_no": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "content-029",
      "lesson_id": "intro-time-commitment",
